'''纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫接触线'''是在1994年5月[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]停火之后成立的軍事分界線，也是此後至[[2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫戰爭|2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫戰爭]]前[[阿爾察赫共和國|阿爾察赫共和國]]與[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]的分界線<ref name="Smolnik">{{cite book|last1=Smolnik|first1=Franziska|title=Secessionist Rule: Protracted Conflict and Configurations of Non-state Authority|date=2016|publisher=Campus Verlag|isbn=9783593506296|page=[https://books.google.am/books?id=TVQBDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA12&dq=Nagorno-Karabakh+line+of+contact&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjkqdjs0dXQAhVCCpoKHY1IBZwQ6AEIOTAH#v=onepage&q=Nagorno-Karabakh%20line%20of%20contact&f=false 12]}}</ref>。纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫接触线北段為[[木罗夫达戈山|木罗夫达戈山]]<ref>{{cite web|title=David Simonyan: Surrender of territories to Azerbaijan: Consequences for Armenia and Nagorno-Karabakh|url=http://www.noravank.am/eng/issues/detail.php?ELEMENT_ID=3470|publisher={{link-en|Noravank Foundation}}|date=21 April 2009 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128165017/http://www.noravank.am/eng/issues/detail.php?ELEMENT_ID=3470 |archivedate=28 November 2019 |quote=the northern flank – by the hard-to-access Mrav mountain range}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Elbakyan|first1=Edgar|title=Արցախի տարածքն անբաժանելի է|url=http://www.hhpress.am/?sub=hodv&hodv=20140516_23&flag=am |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128165554/http://www.hhpress.am/?sub=hodv&hodv=20140516_23&flag=am |archivedate=28 November 2019 
|work={{link-en|Hayastani Hanrapetutyun}}|date=16 May 2014|language=hy|quote=բնական սահմաններ հասցնելու համար, որը հյուսիսում Մռավի լեռնաշղթան է, իսկ հարավում՝ Արաքս գետը}}</ref>。接触线的长度介於180公里至200公里之间。[[2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]爆发後，阿塞拜疆部隊越過接觸線進攻[[阿爾察赫共和國|阿爾察赫共和國]]並佔領該國部分領土，接触线實際上已不復存在。

